ct that the empirical characteristic function may be noisy at high $k$. Consider using a windowing function or smoothing if the empirical $\\phi(k,t)$ shows significant oscillations at high frequencies.' additional_kwargs={} response_metadata={} id='dbe4be20-73ea-41b1-b78e-43b8859a3076'



